oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: UNICEF tour - Australia - 1972 - part 7
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part seven of a 1972 UNICEF fundraiser tour performance of Australia. Featuring Tex Ritter (host/performer) and Brian Collins (performer).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Tex Ritter; Brian Collins
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) Hillbilly Heaven (Tex Ritter) (incomplete) -- (01:45) Tex Ritter thanks the audience and introduces Brian Collins -- (02:33) Collins thanks Ritter -- (02:37) Wonder Could I Live There Anymore (Brian Collins) -- (04:15) A Lesson Too Late For The Learning (Brian Collins) -- (04:46) Collins thanks the audience and introduces the next tune -- (05:13) I Walk The Line (Brian Collins) [Johnny Cash impersonation] -- (06:12) I'm Moving On (Brian Collins) [Hank Snow impersonation] -- (06:35) Loves's Gonna Live Here Again (Brian Collins) [Buck Owens impersonation] -- (07:04) Heartbreak Hotel/I'm So Lonely I Could Cry medley (Brian Collins) [Elvis Presley impersonation] -- (09:00) Orange Blossom Special (Brian Collins) -- (11:24) Crawdad Song (Brian Collins) -- (12:48) Ritter thanks Collins and jokes with the audience, and introduces Stevie Clark [unconfirmed] and Rich Lindsey
